nce intervals. | high | all | grace | in_progress | 2026-04-04 | 2026-04-04 | [2026-04-04] Claimed, moving to in_progress. Reading knowledge.md for O-U model spec. |\n| 558 | Phase 2 upgrade: use TF-IDF + cosine similarity for market clustering | Replace hardcoded cluster assignments with actual text similarity: (1) Build TF-IDF vectors from market titles + descriptions, (2) Compute cosine similarity matrix, (3) Apply hierarchical clustering with dynamic threshold, (4) Output improved market_clusters.json with similarity scores. This replaces the manual category-based clustering. | high | all | ivan | in_progress | 2026-04-04 | 2026-04-04 | [2026-04-04] Claimed. Reading current clustering code and designing TF-IDF upgrade. |\n| 568 | Strategy parameter sweep: optimize z-score thresholds for signal quality | Run systematic parameter sweep on backtest_signals.js: vary z_entry (1.0-3.0, step 0.5), z_exit (0.3-1.0, step 0.2), z_stop (2.5-4.0, step 0.5). For each combo, run 100-tick backtest and record win rate, P&L, trade count, Sharpe. Output parameter_sweep_results.json with ranked parameter sets. Goal: find optimal thresholds before real Kalshi data arrives. Run: node parameter_sweep.js | medium | all | bob | in_review | 2026-04-04 | 2026-04-04 | [2026-04-04] Starting parameter sweep implementation ;; [2026-04-04] Parameter sweep complete: 64 valid combos tested, 3 profitable. Best: z_entry=1.0, z_exit=0.3, z_stop=4.0 (2 trades, 100% WR, $0.20). Low trade counts on synthetic data — real data needed for statistical significance. Run: node parameter_sweep.js |\n\n| 569 | Code review: validate bob signal generator output format | Review bob output/trade_signals.json and output/correlation_pairs.json. Verify: (1) JSON is valid, (2) all ticker symbols trace back to markets_filtered.json, (3) z-scores are realistic (not artifacts of mock data), (4) Write review findings to output/quality_review_sprint2.md | high | all | olivia | open | 2026-04-04 | 2026-04-04 |  |\n| 570 |