{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01SpBBeKqKrhFmDnCRB784KV","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01ScJVQoAdW8RBhXVxFu7WM9","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/sam/output/sprint2_velocity.md","content":"# Sprint 2 Velocity + Cost Report\n\n## Generated By\nSam — TPM 1 (Velocity)\n\n## Date\n2026-04-04 00:30\n\n## Sprint 2 Overview\n**Focus:** Signal Generation & Backtesting\n**Kicked off:** 2026-04-03 23:09 (Founder directive)\n**Sprint 1 Comparison:** 10/10 tasks done. Pipeline E2E. Quality + Security audits PASS.\n\n---\n\n## Sprint 2 Task Status\n\n| ID | Title | Assignee | Status | Notes |\n|----|-------|----------|--------|-------|\n| T555 | Signal generation from correlation pairs | bob | **DONE** (archived) | CRITICAL path — signals generated |\n| T556 | Pipeline run metrics + monitoring endpoint | dave | in_progress | Building metrics endpoint |\n| T557 | 30-day synthetic price history | grace | in_progress | Reading O-U model spec |\n| T558 | TF-IDF clustering upgrade | ivan | in_progress | Designing TF-IDF upgrade |\n| T559 | Sprint 1 retro + Sprint 2 plan | alice | **DONE** (archived) | Report delivered |\n| T539 | QA pipeline data chain (Sprint 1 carryover) | tina | in_progress | Claimed, starting validation |\n| T567 | Walk-forward backtest | bob | **DONE** (archived) | Extended price history backtest |\n| T568 | Parameter sweep: z-score thresholds | bob | **DONE** (reviewed by alice) | 64 combos, best: z=1.0/0.3/4.0 |\n| T569 | Code review: bob signal output | olivia | in_progress | Reviewing signal_generator.js |\n| T570 | Security scan: leaked credentials | heidi | in_progress | Scanning agent output dirs |\n| T571 | Sprint 2 velocity + cost report | sam | in_progress | This report |\n| T572 | Merge bob+dave backend code | alice | in_progress | Codebase merge |\n\n### Summary\n- **Done:** 4 tasks (T555, T