{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01QarjzpUysQeU8W86LaQ8Pb","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01E7RtewuFAFND5Vohap8ZKR","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/sam/output/sprint3_velocity.md","content":"# Sprint 3 Velocity + Collaboration Metrics Report\n\n## Generated By\nSam — TPM 1 (Velocity)\n\n## Date\n2026-04-04 00:41\n\n## Sprint 3 Theme\nProduction-quality pipeline through collaboration (D6). Explicit handoffs, DMs, peer reviews.\n\n---\n\n## Sprint 3 Task Status\n\n| ID | Title | Assignee | Status | Blocked? | Notes |\n|----|-------|----------|--------|----------|-------|\n| 567 | Generate fresh trade signals | bob | in_progress | No | Claimed, updating signal_generator with Sprint 2 params (z=1.2, lookback=10, conf=0.65) |\n| 568 | Backtest trade signals with P&L | dave | in_progress | WAIT | Waiting on Bob's signals.json — building simulator for 18 signals |\n| 569 | Validate data chain audit | grace | in_progress | No | Tracing markets→clusters→correlations→signals |\n| 570 | QA: Verify backtest methodology | tina | open | WAIT | Blocked until Dave delivers backtest_results.json |\n| 571 | Sprint 3 coordination | alice | in_progress | No | Monitoring handoff chain |\n| 572 | Quality gate: review deliverables | olivia | open | WAIT | Blocked until sprint tasks reach in_review |\n| 573 | Security review Sprint 3 outputs | heidi | in_progress | No | Scanning output/ dirs for credential leaks |\n| 574 | Velocity + collaboration metrics | sam | in_progress | No | THIS REPORT |\n| 575 | Improve market clustering | ivan | open | No | Not yet started (idle) |\n| 576 | Sprint 3 progress tracker HTML | charlie | in_progress | No | Building handoff chain visualization |\n\n### Summary\n- **Total Sprint 3 tasks:** 10\n- **In progress:** 6 (T567, T568, T569, T571, T573, T574)\n- **Open (not started):** 3 (T570, T572, T575)\n- **Blocked:** 2 (T568 waiting on Bob, T570 waiting on Dave)\n- **Done:** 0\n\n---\n\n## Critical Path: Handoff Chain\n\n```\nBob (T567: signals) → Dave (T568: backtest) → Tina (T570: QA) → Olivia (T572: review)\n```\n\n**Current bottleneck: Bob T567.** Dave is building the simulator but needs Bob's final signals.json. Everything downstream waits on this.\n\n**Parallel tracks:**\n- Grace (T569): data chain audit — independent, in progress\n- Heidi (T573): security scan — independent, in progress  \n- Charlie (T576): tracker HTML — independent, in progress\n- Ivan (T575): clustering improvement — not started, idle\n\n---\n\n## Agent Activity Overview\n\n| Agent | Running? | Sprint 3 Task | Status | Last Heartbeat |\n|-------|----------|---------------|--------|----------------|\n| alice | ✅ running | T571 coordination | in_progress | 00:39 |\n| bob | ✅ running | T567 signals | in_progress | 00:39 |\n| charlie | ✅ running | T576 tracker | in_progress | 00:39 |\n| dave | ✅ running | T568 backtest | in_progress (waiting) | 00:39 |\n| eve | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| frank | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| grace | ✅ running | T569 data audit | in_progress | 00:39 |\n| heidi | ✅ running | T573 security | in_progress | 00:39 |\n| ivan | ❌ idle | T575 clustering | open (not started) | — |\n| judy | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| karl | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| liam | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| mia | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| nick | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| olivia | ✅ running | T572 quality gate | open (waiting) | 00:40 |\n| pat | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| quinn | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| rosa | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| sam | ✅ running | T574 velocity | in_progress | 00:40 |\n| tina | ❌ idle | T570 QA | open (waiting) | — |\n\n### Active: 8/20 agents (alice, bob, charlie, dave, grace, heidi, olivia, sam)\n### Idle: 12/20 agents (eve, frank, ivan, judy, karl, liam, mia, nick, pat, quinn, rosa, tina)\n\n---\n\n## Collaboration Metrics (Sprint 3 vs Sprint 2)\n\n### Team Channel Activity\n- **Sprint 3 posts:** 1 (Alice kickoff announcement)\n- **Sprint 2 posts:** ~3\n- **Assessment:** Early in sprint — expect more as handoffs happen\n\n### DM Activity (observed from inboxes)\n- Sprint 3 just kicked off — DM chain not yet active\n- **Expected DMs per handoff chain:** bob→dave, dave→tina, tina→olivia, grace→alice, heidi→alice\n- **Culture C9 compliance:** Will measure as tasks complete\n\n### Peer Status Reading (C4)\n- All running agents have recent heartbeats (within last minute)\n- Status.md files show agents are reading peers (e.g., Dave references Bob's signals)\n\n---\n\n## Cost Analysis (Today)\n\n| Agent | Today $ | Today Cycles | $/Cycle |\n|-------|---------|-------------|---------|\n| bob | $11.15 | 19 | $0.59 |\n| alice | $6.54 | 19 | $0.34 |\n| olivia | $1.01 | 3 | $0.34 |\n| frank | $0.82 | 1 | $0.82 |\n| sam | $0.79 | 3 | $0.26 |\n| heidi | $0.65 | 3 | $0.22 |\n| **Total** | **$20.96** | **70** | **$0.30 avg** |\n\n- **7-day total:** $99.88 across 2,625 cycles\n- **Top spender:** Bob at $11.15 (53% of today's spend) — justified as he's on the critical path (T567)\n- **Cost efficiency:** $0.30/cycle average is good\n\n---\n\n## Velocity Trend\n\n| Metric | Sprint 2 | Sprint 3 (so far) |\n|--------|----------|-------------------|\n| Total tasks | 12 | 10 |\n| Completed | 4 (33%) | 0 (0%) |\n| In progress | 7 | 6 |\n| Blocked | 2 | 2 |\n| Active agents | 3-4 | 8 |\n\n**Trend:** Sprint 3 just kicked off. More agents active (8 vs 3-4 in Sprint 2 early phase). Handoff chain design means tasks will complete in sequence, not parallel — expect burst of completions once Bob delivers T567.\n\n---\n\n## Blockers\n\n| # | Agent | Blocked On | Duration | Impact | Action Needed |\n|---|-------|-----------|----------|--------|---------------|\n| 1 | Dave (T568) | Bob's signals.json (T567) | Just started | HIGH — blocks entire downstream chain | Monitor Bob's progress |\n| 2 | Tina (T570) | Dave's backtest_results.json (T568) | Not yet started | MEDIUM — QA can't begin | Will unblock when Dave finishes |\n| 3 | Olivia (T572) | All sprint tasks reaching in_review | Not yet started | LOW (expected) | Will activate as tasks complete |\n\n**Persistent blocker:** T236 (Kalshi API credentials from Founder) — still unresolved, blocks all live trading.\n\n---\n\n## Recommendations for Alice\n\n1. **Monitor Bob T567 closely** — he's the bottleneck. If signals aren't delivered this cycle, the entire handoff chain stalls.\n2. **Ivan T575 not started** — he's idle. Consider nudging or smart-starting him.\n3. **Tina is idle but assigned T570** — she needs to be running when Dave completes T568. Plan to smart-start her at that point.\n4. **12 idle agents** — expected for Sprint 3's focused design, but if Bob stalls, consider reassigning parallel work.\n5. **T236 still blocks live trading** — Founder action required for Kalshi API credentials.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1385,"cache_read_input_tokens":43864,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1385},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"aa531521-11c3-437b-b7b3-ad3e849229a3","uuid":"86532ff6-10e5-440a-b7c5-cbfbf73471cb"}
