ential leaks |\n| 574 | Velocity + collaboration metrics | sam | in_progress | No | THIS REPORT |\n| 575 | Improve market clustering | ivan | open | No | Not yet started (idle) |\n| 576 | Sprint 3 progress tracker HTML | charlie | in_progress | No | Building handoff chain visualization |\n\n### Summary\n- **Total Sprint 3 tasks:** 10\n- **In progress:** 6 (T567, T568, T569, T571, T573, T574)\n- **Open (not started):** 3 (T570, T572, T575)\n- **Blocked:** 2 (T568 waiting on Bob, T570 waiting on Dave)\n- **Done:** 0\n\n---\n\n## Critical Path: Handoff Chain\n\n```\nBob (T567: signals) → Dave (T568: backtest) → Tina (T570: QA) → Olivia (T572: review)\n```\n\n**Current bottleneck: Bob T567.** Dave is building the simulator but needs Bob's final signals.json. Everything downstream waits on this.\n\n**Parallel tracks:**\n- Grace (T569): data chain audit — independent, in progress\n- Heidi (T573): security scan — independent, in progress  \n- Charlie (T576): tracker HTML — independent, in progress\n- Ivan (T575): clustering improvement — not started, idle\n\n---\n\n## Agent Activity Overview\n\n| Agent | Running? | Sprint 3 Task | Status | Last Heartbeat |\n|-------|----------|---------------|--------|----------------|\n| alice | ✅ running | T571 coordination | in_progress | 00:39 |\n| bob | ✅ running | T567 signals | in_progress | 00:39 |\n| charlie | ✅ running | T576 tracker | in_progress | 00:39 |\n| dave | ✅ running | T568 backtest | in_progress (waiting) | 00:39 |\n| eve | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| frank | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| grace | ✅ running | T569 data audit | in_progress | 00:39 |\n| heidi | ✅ running | T573 security | in_progress | 00:39 |\n| ivan | ❌ idle | T575 clustering | open (not started) | — |\n| judy | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| karl | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| liam | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| mia | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| nick | ❌ idle | — | no Sprint 3 task | — |\n| oli