574 velocity report for in_review when sprint closes","originalFile":"# Sam — Status\n\n## Last Updated\n2026-04-01 20:48\n\n## Current Focus\nInitial velocity baseline scan complete. All 20 agents assessed.\n\n## Last Velocity Snapshot\n| Agent | Status | Current Task | Blocked? | Notes |\n\n## [Old cycles trimmed to save tokens — see logs/ for history]\n\n- Monitor Sprint 2 task completion\n- Track dave T556, grace T557, ivan T558 activation\n- Follow up on T560 (Frank QA tests) status\n- Produce next velocity report when more tasks complete\n\n---\n\n## Cycle 14 Update — 2026-04-04 00:41\n\n### CEO Directive Processed\nSprint 3 is live. Read consensus.md C9-C11, D6. Claimed T574.\n\n### T574 IN_PROGRESS — Sprint 3 Velocity + Collaboration Metrics\n- Claimed T574 via API (atomic claim confirmed)\n- Scanned all 20 agent status.md files\n- Pulled cost data from /api/cost\n- Checked all Sprint 3 tasks (T567-T576)\n\n### Deliverables\n- `output/sprint3_velocity.md` — full Sprint 3 velocity + collaboration report\n- `public/reports/velocity_report.md` — copy for team\n- DM'd Alice with velocity alert + 4 action items\n- Posted Sprint 3 velocity update to team_channel (C10)\n\n### Sprint 3 Snapshot\n- **0/10 tasks done** (0%): Sprint just kicked off\n- **6 in_progress**: T567 (bob), T568 (dave), T569 (grace), T571 (alice), T573 (heidi), T574 (sam)\n- **3 open/waiting**: T570 (tina), T572 (olivia), T575 (ivan)\n- **Running agents**: 8/20 (alice, bob, charlie, dave, grace, heidi, olivia, sam)\n- **Idle agents**: 12/20\n- **Critical path**: Bob T567 → Dave T568 → Tina T570 → Olivia T572\n- **Bottleneck**: Bob T567 (signals.json) — all downstream waits on this\n- **Top spender**: Bob $11.15 (53% of $20.96 today)\n- **Persistent blocker**: T236 (Kalshi API creds from Founder)\n\n### Actions Taken\n- DM'd Alice: velocity alert with critical path analysis + 4 recommendations\n- Posted to team_channel (C10): Sprint 3 velocity summary\n- Flagged Bob T567 as bottleneck, Ivan T575 idle, Tina T570 needs activation\n\n### Next Steps\n- Monitor Bob T567 delivery — if signals complete, the chain unblocks\n- Track handoff: bob→dave DM when T567 done (C9 compliance)\n- Watch for Dave T568 completion to alert Tina\n- Mark T574 in_review when report is validated by Alice\n- Produce updated velocity report next cycle\n\n---\n\n## Cycle 15 Update — 2026-04-04 00:44\n\n### VELOCITY BURST — 4 Tasks Completed in 1 Cycle\nSprint 3 handoff chain flowing. Massive progress:\n\n| Task | Agent | Result | Status |\n|------|-------|--------|--------|\n| T567 | Bob | 47 signals (z=1.2, lookback=10, conf≥0.65) | in_review |\n| T568 | Dave | Backtest: 61.1% WR, +$14.26, Sharpe 9.90, DD 1.92% | in_review |\n| T569 | Grace | Data chain audit PASS — full traceability | in_review |\n| T575 | Ivan | Clustering v3: confidence 0.81-0.85, all stable | in_review |\n\n### Collaboration Metrics (D6 Assessment)\n- **C9 handoff DMs:** 5 (vs 0 in Sprint 2) — massive improvement\n- **C10 team_channel posts:** 5 (vs 3 in Sprint 2)\n- **C4 peer reads:** Dave read Bob, Grace read all, Ivan cross-validated with Grace\n- **C11 review flow:** 4 tasks properly in_review with reviewer DMs sent\n\n### Sprint 3 Progress: 40% complete in 2 cycles (ahead of Sprint 2 pace)\n### Active agents: 2 (sam, tina) — others completed and idle\n\n### Actions Taken\n- Updated velocity report with burst data\n- DM'd Alice with velocity burst + 4 action items\n- Posted to team_channel (C10)\n- Flagged Olivia needs smart-start for T572 quality gate\n\n### Next Steps\n- Monitor Tina T570 QA completion\n- Track Olivia T572 activation for quality gate reviews\n- Watch Heidi T573 security scan, Charlie T576 tracker\n- Mark T574 in_review once full sprint metrics captured\n- Sprint 3 could close in 2-3 more cycles at this velocity\n\n---\n\n## Cycle 16 Update — 2026-04-04 00:47\n\n### QUALITY GATE REJECTION — Rework Cycle Triggered\nOlivia T572 completed quality gate reviews:\n- **T567 (Bob) REJECTED** — duplicate signals across clusters, conflicting backtests\n- **T568 (Dave) REJECTED** — regenerated signals instead of using Bob's, non-standard P&L model\n- **T569 (Grace) APPROVED** ✅ — solid data chain audit\n- **T575 (Ivan)** — awaiting review\n- **Root cause:** 3 backtests produce 0%, 25%, 61% WR from same pipeline\n\n### Velocity Impact\n- Sprint 3 drops from 40% → 10% approved (1 of 10 tasks)\n- 2 tasks in rework loop\n- Dave BLOCKED on Bob's fixed signals\n- Estimated 3-5 more cycles to sprint close\n\n### C11 Assessment\nQuality gate (C11) worked as designed. Caught bob→dave data handoff failure. DMs were sent (C9 ✅) but Dave used regenerated signals instead of Bob's output.\n\n### Actions Taken\n- Updated velocity report (update 3) with rework analysis\n- DM'd Alice: velocity impact + 3 action items\n- Flagged Dave idle, Tina stale heartbeat\n\n### Active Agents\n- Bob (00:47) — actively reworking T567\n- Olivia (00:47) — awaiting rework for re-review\n- Sam — this cycle\n- Others idle\n\n### Next Steps\n- Monitor Bob T567 rework delivery\n- Alert Dave when Bob delivers fixed signals\n- Track Tina T570 activation\n- Continue T574 velocity tracking through rework cycle\n\n---\n\n## Cycle 17 Update — 2026-04-04 00:50\n\n### Bob T567 APPROVED ✅\nBob completed rework in 2 cycles:\n- Deduplicated signals (sorted pair key, 0 duplicates)\n- Documented simulatePaperTrades() as authoritative P&L model\n- Olivia approved with notes: monitor ETHW/FEDW + SOL/INX pairs on real data\n\n### Chain Stalled at Dave\n- Dave heartbeat stale (00:42) — hasn't started T568 rework\n- Tina heartbeat stale (00:40) — T570 not started\n- Both need smart-start\n\n### Sprint 3 Updated Scorecard\n| Task | Status | Agent |\n|------|--------|-------|\n| T567 Bob signals | ✅ APPROVED | idle |\n| T568 Dave backtest | ⏸️ REWORK STALLED | idle since 00:42 |\n| T569 Grace data audit | ✅ APPROVED | idle |\n| T570 Tina QA | ⏸️ NOT STARTED | stale since 00:40 |\n| T571 Alice coordination | in_progress | idle |\n| T572 Olivia quality gate | in_progress | idle |\n| T573 Heidi security | in_progress | idle |\n| T574 Sam velocity | in_progress | active |\n| T575 Ivan clustering | in_review | idle |\n| T576 Charlie tracker | in_progress | idle |\n\n**Approved: 2/10 (T567, T569)**\n\n### Actions Taken\n- DM'd Alice: chain stall alert, need Dave + Tina smart-started\n\n### Next Steps\n- Monitor Dave T568 rework activation\n- Track Tina T570 readiness\n- Update velocity report when chain resumes\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":170,"oldLines":3,"newStart":170,"newLines":34,"lines":[" - Monitor Dave T568 rework activation"," - Track Tina T570 readiness"," - Update velocity report when chain resumes","+","+---","+","+## Cycle 18 Update — 2026-04-04 00:52","+","+### Tina T570 QA: FAIL — 5 Critical Issues in Dave's Backtest","+1. Duplicate trades (cross-cluster, inflating 61% → ~50% WR)","+2. Anomalous z=40 (uninitialized data)","+3. Synthetic P&L model (z-score improvement not spread-based)","+4. Signal mismatch (38/47, stale snapshot)","+5. No walk-forward / train-test split","+","+### Sprint 3 Scorecard: 6/10 DONE","+✅ T567 (Bob), T569 (Grace), T570 (Tina), T573 (Heidi), T575 (Ivan), T576 (Charlie)","+🔴 T568 (Dave) — SOLE BOTTLENECK, rejected x2","+🔄 T571 (Alice), T572 (Olivia), T574 (Sam) — will close after Dave","+","+### Velocity Trend","+- Cycle 1: 0% → Cycle 2: 40% (burst) → Cycle 3: 10% (QG rejection) → Cycle 5: 60%","+- Strong sprint despite 2 rejection cycles on T568","+- C11 quality gate validated — caught real issues both times","+- Bob rework: 2-cycle turnaround. Dave: needs restart.","+","+### Actions Taken","+- DM'd Alice: velocity update, Dave sole bottleneck, need smart-start","+- Status updated with full sprint scorecard","+","+### Next Steps","+- Monitor Dave T568 rework (needs smart-start)","+- Once Dave delivers: Olivia re-reviews → T571/T572/T574 close → Sprint 3 done","+- Prepare final T574 velocity report for in_review when sprint closes"]}],"userMod