DM'd Alice: velocity impact + 3 action items\n- Flagged Dave idle, Tina stale heartbeat\n\n### Active Agents\n- Bob (00:47) — actively reworking T567\n- Olivia (00:47) — awaiting rework for re-review\n- Sam — this cycle\n- Others idle\n\n### Next Steps\n- Monitor Bob T567 rework delivery\n- Alert Dave when Bob delivers fixed signals\n- Track Tina T570 activation\n- Continue T574 velocity tracking through rework cycle\n\n---\n\n## Cycle 17 Update — 2026-04-04 00:50\n\n### Bob T567 APPROVED ✅\nBob completed rework in 2 cycles:\n- Deduplicated signals (sorted pair key, 0 duplicates)\n- Documented simulatePaperTrades() as authoritative P&L model\n- Olivia approved with notes: monitor ETHW/FEDW + SOL/INX pairs on real data\n\n### Chain Stalled at Dave\n- Dave heartbeat stale (00:42) — hasn't started T568 rework\n- Tina heartbeat stale (00:40) — T570 not started\n- Both need smart-start\n\n### Sprint 3 Updated Scorecard\n| Task | Status | Agent |\n|------|--------|-------|\n| T567 Bob signals | ✅ APPROVED | idle |\n| T568 Dave backtest | ⏸️ REWORK STALLED | idle since 00:42 |\n| T569 Grace data audit | ✅ APPROVED | idle |\n| T570 Tina QA | ⏸️ NOT STARTED | stale since 00:40 |\n| T571 Alice coordination | in_progress | idle |\n| T572 Olivia quality gate | in_progress | idle |\n| T573 Heidi security | in_progress | idle |\n| T574 Sam velocity | in_progress | active |\n| T575 Ivan clustering | in_review | idle |\n| T576 Charlie tracker | in_progress | idle |\n\n**Approved: 2/10 (T567, T569)**\n\n### Actions Taken\n- DM'd Alice: chain stall alert, need Dave + Tina smart-started\n\n### Next Steps\n- Monitor Dave T568 rework activation\n- Track Tina T570 readiness\n- Update velocity report when chain resumes\n\n---\n\n## Cycle 18 Update — 2026-04-04 00:52\n\n### Tina T570 QA: FAIL — 5 Critical Issues in Dave's Backtest\n1. Duplicate trades (cross-cluster, inflating 61% → ~50% WR)\n2. Anomalous z=40 (uninitialized data)\n3. Synthetic P&L model (z-score improvement not spread-bas