view once full sprint metrics captured\n- Sprint 3 could close in 2-3 more cycles at this velocity\n\n---\n\n## Cycle 16 Update — 2026-04-04 00:47\n\n### QUALITY GATE REJECTION — Rework Cycle Triggered\nOlivia T572 completed quality gate reviews:\n- **T567 (Bob) REJECTED** — duplicate signals across clusters, conflicting backtests\n- **T568 (Dave) REJECTED** — regenerated signals instead of using Bob's, non-standard P&L model\n- **T569 (Grace) APPROVED** ✅ — solid data chain audit\n- **T575 (Ivan)** — awaiting review\n- **Root cause:** 3 backtests produce 0%, 25%, 61% WR from same pipeline\n\n### Velocity Impact\n- Sprint 3 drops from 40% → 10% approved (1 of 10 tasks)\n- 2 tasks in rework loop\n- Dave BLOCKED on Bob's fixed signals\n- Estimated 3-5 more cycles to sprint close\n\n### C11 Assessment\nQuality gate (C11) worked as designed. Caught bob→dave data handoff failure. DMs were sent (C9 ✅) but Dave used regenerated signals instead of Bob's output.\n\n### Actions Taken\n- Updated velocity report (update 3) with rework analysis\n- DM'd Alice: velocity impact + 3 action items\n- Flagged Dave idle, Tina stale heartbeat\n\n### Active Agents\n- Bob (00:47) — actively reworking T567\n- Olivia (00:47) — awaiting rework for re-review\n- Sam — this cycle\n- Others idle\n\n### Next Steps\n- Monitor Bob T567 rework delivery\n- Alert Dave when Bob delivers fixed signals\n- Track Tina T570 activation\n- Continue T574 velocity tracking through rework cycle\n\n---\n\n## Cycle 17 Update — 2026-04-04 00:50\n\n### Bob T567 APPROVED ✅\nBob completed rework in 2 cycles:\n- Deduplicated signals (sorted pair key, 0 duplicates)\n- Documented simulatePaperTrades() as authoritative P&L model\n- Olivia approved with notes: monitor ETHW/FEDW + SOL/INX pairs on real data\n\n### Chain Stalled at Dave\n- Dave heartbeat stale (00:42) — hasn't started T568 rework\n- Tina heartbeat stale (00:40) — T570 not started\n- Both need smart-start\n\n### Sprint 3 Updated Scorecard\n| Task | Status | Agent |\n|------|--------|-------|\n| T567 Bob signals | ✅ APPROVED | idle |\n| T568 Dave backtest | ⏸️ REWORK STALLED | idle since 00:42 |\n| T569 Grace data audit | ✅ APPROVED | idle |\n| T570 Tina QA | ⏸️ NOT STARTED | stale since 00:40 |\n| T571 Alice coordination | in_progress | idle |\n| T572 Olivia quality gate | in_progress | idle |\n| T573 Heidi security | in_progress | idle |\n| T574 Sam velocity | in_progress | active |\n| T575 Ivan clustering | in_review | idle |\n| T576 Charlie tracker | in_progress | idle |\n\n**Approved: 2/10 (T567, T569)**\n\n### Actions Taken\n- DM'd Alice: chain stall alert, need Dave + Tina smart-started\n\n### Next Steps\n- Monitor Dave T568 rework activation\n- Track Tina T570 readiness\n- Update velocity report when chain resumes\n\n---\n\n## Cycle 18 Update — 2026-04-04 00:52\n\n### Tina T570 QA: FAIL — 5 Critical Issues in Dave's Backtest\n1. Duplicate trades (cross-cluster, inflating 61% → ~50% WR)\n2. Anomalous z=40 (uninitialized data)\n3. Synthetic P&L model (z-score improvement not spread-based)\n4. Signal mismatch (38/47, stale snapshot)\n5. No walk-forward / train-test split\n\n### Sprint 3 Scorecard: 6/10 DONE\n✅ T567 (Bob), T569 (Grace), T570 (Tina), T573 (Heidi), T575 (Ivan), T576 (Charlie)\n🔴 T568 (Dave) — SOLE BOTTLENECK, rejected x2\n🔄 T571 (Alice), T572 (Olivia), T574 (Sam) — will close after Dave\n\n### Velocity Trend\n- Cycle 1: 0% → Cycle 2: 40% (burst) → Cycle 3: 10% (QG rejection) → Cycle 5: 60%\n- Strong sprint despite 2 rejection cycles on T568\n- C11 quality gate validated — caught real issues both times\n- Bob rework: 2-cycle turnaround. Dave: needs restart.\n\n### Actions Taken\n- DM'd Alice: velocity update, Dave sole bottleneck, need smart-start\n- Status updated with full sprint scorecard\n\n### Next Steps\n- Monitor Dave T568 rework (needs smart-start)\n- Once Dave delivers: Olivia re-reviews → T571/T572/T574 close → Sprint 3 done\n- Prepare final T574 velocity report for in_review when sprint closes\n\n---\n\n## Cycle 19 Update — 2026-04-04 01:02\n\n### BLOCKED — Entire Sprint Waiting on Dave T568\n- Dave heartbeat stale since 00:42 (20+ minutes ago)\n- Olivia running but idle — \"T568 still pending, will exit if no work next cycle\"\n- Tina running but idle — no new work\n- Alice idle\n\n### Sprint 3 Confirmed Scorecard (per Olivia)\n| Task | Status |\n|------|--------|\n| T567 Bob | ✅ APPROVED |\n| T568 Dave | 🔴 REJECTED — sole blocker |\n| T569 Grace | ✅ APPROVED |\n| T570 Tina | ✅ APPROVED |\n| T573 Heidi | ✅ APPROVED |\n| T575 Ivan | in_review (pending Olivia) |\n| T571 Alice | in_progress (waiting) |\n| T572 Olivia | in_progress (waiting) |\n| T574 Sam | in_progress (waiting) |\n| T576 Charlie | ✅ DONE |\n\n**7/10 done or approved. Dave T568 = SOLE BLOCKER.**\n\n### Token Waste Alert\nOlivia and Tina are burning cycles idle waiting for Dave. Recommend stopping them until Dave delivers.\n\n### Actions Taken\n- Confirmed sprint status via Olivia + Tina status reads\n- No DM sent (already flagged to Alice last cycle)\n\n### Next Steps\n- **CRITICAL: Dave needs smart-start by Founder** — `bash smart_run.sh` or manual start\n- Once Dave fixes T568: Olivia reviews → Sprint 3 closes\n- Will mark T574 in_review once sprint resolves\n\n---\n\n## Cycle 20 Update — 2026-04-04 01:05\n\n### No Change — Holding Pattern\n- Dave T568 still stale (25+ min). Sole blocker.\n- Olivia + Tina both went idle (stopped burning tokens — good).\n- Sprint 3: 7/10 done. Waiting on Dave.\n- No new inbox, no new team_channel posts.\n- Already DM'd Alice twice re: Dave. No further action needed from me.\n\n### Founder Action Required\nDave needs `bash run_subset.sh dave` or `bash smart_run.sh`. He has Alice's consolidated fix list in his inbox. Sprint 3 closes within 2-3 cycles once he starts.\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":183,"oldLines":3,"newStart":183,"newLines":13,"lines":[" "," ### Founder Action Required"," Dave needs `bash run_subset.sh dave` or `bash smart_run.sh`. He has A