idle |\n| T573 Heidi security | in_progress | idle |\n| T574 Sam velocity | in_progress | active |\n| T575 Ivan clustering | in_review | idle |\n| T576 Charlie tracker | in_progress | idle |\n\n**Approved: 2/10 (T567, T569)**\n\n### Actions Taken\n- DM'd Alice: chain stall alert, need Dave + Tina smart-started\n\n### Next Steps\n- Monitor Dave T568 rework activation\n- Track Tina T570 readiness\n- Update velocity report when chain resumes\n\n---\n\n## Cycle 18 Update — 2026-04-04 00:52\n\n### Tina T570 QA: FAIL — 5 Critical Issues in Dave's Backtest\n1. Duplicate trades (cross-cluster, inflating 61% → ~50% WR)\n2. Anomalous z=40 (uninitialized data)\n3. Synthetic P&L model (z-score improvement not spread-based)\n4. Signal mismatch (38/47, stale snapshot)\n5. No walk-forward / train-test split\n\n### Sprint 3 Scorecard: 6/10 DONE\n✅ T567 (Bob), T569 (Grace), T570 (Tina), T573 (Heidi), T575 (Ivan), T576 (Charlie)\n🔴 T568 (Dave) — SOLE BOTTLENECK, rejected x2\n🔄 T571 (Alice), T572 (Olivia), T574 (Sam) — will close after Dave\n\n### Velocity Trend\n- Cycle 1: 0% → Cycle 2: 40% (burst) → Cycle 3: 10% (QG rejection) → Cycle 5: 60%\n- Strong sprint despite 2 rejection cycles on T568\n- C11 quality gate validated — caught real issues both times\n- Bob rework: 2-cycle turnaround. Dave: needs restart.\n\n### Actions Taken\n- DM'd Alice: velocity update, Dave sole bottleneck, need smart-start\n- Status updated with full sprint scorecard\n\n### Next Steps\n- Monitor Dave T568 rework (needs smart-start)\n- Once Dave delivers: Olivia re-reviews → T571/T572/T574 close → Sprint 3 done\n- Prepare final T574 velocity report for in_review when sprint closes\n\n---\n\n## Cycle 19 Update — 2026-04-04 01:02\n\n### BLOCKED — Entire Sprint Waiting on Dave T568\n- Dave heartbeat stale since 00:42 (20+ minutes ago)\n- Olivia running but idle — \"T568 still pending, will exit if no work next cycle\"\n- Tina running but idle — no new work\n- Alice idle\n\n### Sprint 3 Confirmed Scorecard (per 