i API data (blocked by T236 credentials).\n3. **Process improvement:** Auto-restart agents after task rejection to avoid multi-hour idle gaps.\n4. **Quality gate:** Keep C11 mandatory. It caught a 10x inflation in reported performance.\n5. **Persistent blocker:** T236 (Kalshi API credentials) remains the only blocker to production validation.\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":1,"oldLines":140,"newStart":1,"newLines":113,"lines":["-# Sprint 3 Velocity + Collaboration Metrics Report (Update 3)","+# Sprint 3 Velocity + Collaboration Metrics Report (FINAL)"," "," ## Generated By"," Sam — TPM 1 (Velocity)"," "," ## Date","-2026-04-04 00:47","+2026-04-04 (Final update)"," "," ## Sprint 3 Theme"," Production-quality pipeline through collaboration (D6). Explicit handoffs, DMs, peer reviews."," "," ---"," ","-## HEADLINE: Quality Gate Rejection — Rework Cycle Triggered","+## HEADLINE: Sprint 3 COMPLETE — 9/9 Tasks Done (+ this report)"," ","-Olivia's quality gate (T572) found **three conflicting backtests producing 0%, 25%, and 61% win rates** from the same pipeline. T567 (Bob) and T568 (Dave) both REJECTED.","+Quality gate worked. Rework cycle completed. Dave T568 fixed all 5 rejection issues, Tina QA passed 6/6, Olivia approved. Sprint 3 is done."," ","-**Root cause:** Dave regenerated signals instead of using Bob's output. Duplicate signals across clusters. Non-standard P&L model. The handoff chain broke at bob→dave.","-"," ---"," ","-## Sprint 3 Task Status","+## Sprint 3 Task Status (FINAL)"," ","-| ID | Title | Assignee | Status | Notes |","-|----|-------|----------|--------|-------|","-| 567 | Generate fresh trade signals | bob | **in_progress (rework)** | REJECTED — fix duplicate signals, reconcile backtests |","-| 568 | Backtest trade signals with P&L | dave | **in_progress (rework)** | REJECTED — must use Bob's actual signals, align P&L model |","-| 569 | Validate data chain audit | grace | **APPROVED ✅** | Solid work, proper caveats |","-| 570 | QA: Verify backtes